  lines:
  - speakerId: good
    text: Home - work, work - home every day, every week, every month, every year.
      And where does this lead you? To a choice between the left and right ledges.
      Which one will be your lucky ticket? Should you follow the beaten path and
      trust your past choices, or take a risk in the hopes of change?
